EXTRACTED VALUE: ET: QW is not fun, period.
Nothing more than a standard hack n’ slash adventure. Glitches, poor A.I., and generic gameplay all contribute to Too Human lackluster showing.
Everything The Outfit does has been done better on lesser hardware.
Spend about 30 minutes to an hour of time with this game and you will realize that the makers of EDF just didn’t put their all into the title.
